# Tank Install Calculator - Privacy Policy

Last updated: July 15, 2026

## Overview
Tank Install Calculator is committed to protecting your privacy. This app does not collect, store, or share any personal information.

## Data Collection
This app does NOT collect any data from users, including but not limited to:
- Personal information
- Location data
- Usage analytics
- Device information
- Contacts or photos

## Data Storage
All calculations performed in this app are processed locally on your device. No data is transmitted to external servers or third parties.

## Sharing
When you use the Share button to export calculation results, the data is shared only through your device's native sharing mechanism (Messages, Email, etc.). We do not receive or store any shared information.

## Children's Privacy
This app does not knowingly collect information from children under 13 years of age.

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the app and on this page.

